                <h1>Discover the Life and Works of C.S. Lewis</h1>
                <p>C.S. Lewis was a renowned British writer and theologian, best known for his works such as "The Chronicles of Narnia" and "Mere Christianity." His writings explored deep philosophical and spiritual themes, making profound impacts on literature and Christian thought. Lewis’s blend of imagination and theology continues to inspire readers worldwide.</p>
